ways. And I've met authors who could think of very witty, very original things

02:00.140 --> 02:09.100
to write in every book, but I'd freeze up. I'm glad to sign my name, but I can't
be creative there on the spur of the moment, so I usually end up saying good

02:09.100 --> 02:21.800
luck, best wishes, best ever, and do that repeatedly. So that part was
realistic. Why are science fiction authors so accessible to the fans, Whereas,

02:22.080 --> 02:25.240
as you mentioned, in other genres, they're not. I have no idea.

