think there's certainly room for both. I think both fulfill needs of people. I

03:37.240 --> 03:49.880
keep telling mundane kind of people, mainstream kind of people, who ask about,
what do I purpose, or what good is science fiction? And I keep saying, well,

03:50.000 --> 04:00.060
people have always wanted myths. They have always wanted wonderful creatures.
They sit around the campfire and they would fantasize about the creatures that

04:00.060 --> 04:09.800
lived in the next country. Well, this whole planet, we know what's in the next
country on this planet. The monsters are in outer space, or the myths can be in

04:09.800 --> 04:21.480
outer space. They're also in inner space. It's the same reason that I think the
vampires and horror stories have come up because that's where people can go to

04:21.480 --> 04:31.880
for myths now. I don't know what it is in people that want these wonderful
monsters, but they will have them. They don't care if the world is settled. Why,

04:31.940 --> 04:44.200
