might exist, people that want to reach out can reach out for strange and

04:44.200 --> 04:55.720
wonderful creatures beyond space and the ones that don't want to reach out can
reach for the creatures in inner space I think it also has to do with a lot of

04:55.720 --> 05:07.700
the time um the space that things are very complex they're very frightening
there are no clear cut rights and wrongs and there's really no answers to lots

05:07.700 --> 05:22.320
