worlds where there are clear rights and clear wrongs where you can end their

05:59.160 --> 06:15.540
problems with a strong right arm and a magic sword and a pure heart. And I think
that the heroic fantasy then gives people something to get away from, to get

06:15.540 --> 06:24.240
away from this world, like a lot of these movies that they were producing during
the Depression and a lot of the books that they were writing during the

06:24.240 --> 06:35.180
Depression, adventure stories, so the people could get away from the terrible
things that they had to face every day. And I think that's why there's a lot of

06:35.180 --> 06:43.500
fantasy. And I think there's a need for it. And I think it's wonderful that it's
there for the people who want it. And there's probably a lot of bad fantasy

06:43.500 --> 06:53.460
